name: Mini Accordion Album
description:
Mini Accordion Albums are 3 inches x 3 inches printed professional on standard matte paper, 0.24mm thick. The albums hold together with a hidden magnet. 

Albums are fully customizable with your images, your choice of text, and you can also change the colours if you like.

To order please visit http://www.cardsalbumsandmore.com gallery to view all the mini accordion album options available. 

Please contact me via email (christine@bezansonphotography.com) to arrange the images you would like to choose for you mini album.

name: Session Deposit
description:
This is to purchase your retainer/deposit to hold your session date with Bezanson Photography. 

The deposit is non-refundable however in the event you cannot make it, you are welcome to have these funds credited towards a future session.

If you have any questions please call (780-977-0828) or email me at christine@bezansonphotography.com

name: GIVE THE GIFT OF ART | $100 GIFT CERTIFICATE
description:

name: CUSTOM IPHONE 4, 4S & 5 COVERS & SKINS
description:
Display your favorite image with an amazing personalized iPhone case or skin! 

The covers and skins are compatible with iphone 4, 4s, and 5.

The iPhone covers are plastic and cover the entire back of the phone (expect the cutout for the camera lens).

iPhone skins are vinyl with a gloss laminate and adhere to the back of your iPhone.

When ordering please leave the CASE NUMBER , IMAGE/FILE NUMBER OF PHOTO, as well as any TEXT in the comments box so I know which image you wish to have printed onto your cover or skin.

Cases and skins will be shipped to your door :)

name: 5x7 Little Black Book
description:
5x7 Album boasts a beautiful textured cover with 0.8mm right photo paper pages. Each page is printed on real photo paper with a lay flat design. Albums are stain free as they have a protective coating  to ensure a lifetime of durability.

Albums will include 20 personal images with the option to add more for an additional $2.00 per page.
